{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-04-11-how-to-add-arabic-text-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aHoisting! To add arabic text in react js, you can write Arabic text in html tag`. It will add arabic text in react js. Today, I am…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add arabic text in react js, you can write Arabic text in html tag`. It will add arabic text in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add arabic text in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let’s start with the first step.</p>\n<h2>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h2>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 2: Import react component.</h2>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 3: Create a Component.</h2>\n<p>you can write Arabic text in html tag and add arabic text in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h2<span class=\"token operator\">></span>مرحبا بالعالم<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h2<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>هذا هو نص باللغة العربية في React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Define the add arabic text example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">React</code> and you can write Arabic text in html tag, to add arabic text in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h2<span class=\"token operator\">></span>مرحبا بالعالم<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h2<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>هذا هو نص باللغة العربية في React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have wrote Arabic text in html tag and add arabic text in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 341px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e6bf2ab6f6f2edbcacf8b65a71d39d40/5af35/add-arabic-text.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.78481012658227%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRloAAABXRUJQVlA4IE4AAACwAwCdASoUAA8APtFWpEuoJKOhsAgBABoJQBOkBLhijeuDupb3AADyp4vtJ4qyVxpmGmzNZErn7b93fmISmMaiHu+v4nkGe4SW7LwYAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, arabic text\"\n        title=\"React, add, arabic text\"\n        src=\"/static/e6bf2ab6f6f2edbcacf8b65a71d39d40/5af35/add-arabic-text.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e6bf2ab6f6f2edbcacf8b65a71d39d40/81b7c/add-arabic-text.webp 158w,\n/static/e6bf2ab6f6f2edbcacf8b65a71d39d40/6ea66/add-arabic-text.webp 315w,\n/static/e6bf2ab6f6f2ed